<a href="/questions/242148-can-anyone-recommend-a-similar-style-of">Can anyone recommend a similar style of writing - humorous- but written by a woman? Beyond Ellen Degeneres, Lena Dunham, Tina Fey et al and more along the lines of Kingsley Amis, J.D. Salinger, or even David Niven.</a>
