</a><br/>But prefers to get paid </span>
  <span id="freeText4871757681892335375" style="display:none">Find all of my reviews at: <a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="http://52bookminimum.blogspot.com/">http://52bookminimum.blogspot.com/</a><br><br>The funniest collection by David Sedaris that I’ve read so far. There just aren’t words to express how happy these books make me. Sedaris is by far my favorite humorist/essayist/columnist/whatever-ist you want to call him. His writing can turn my frown upside down and always leaves me laughing like a lunatic. <br><br>My infatuation actually began with another Sedaris – David’s sister Amy. Anyone who looks like this:<br><a href="http://imgur.com/pb6IzeN" rel="nofollow noopener">
