        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3242940966" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4934933371849509458">In my binge listening to Sedaris lately, looking for laughs and something to lighten my day I didn&apos;t find this selection of essays as humorous as the 3 previous books. I even went through it a second time to be sure. There were definitely some funny moments and some chuckles to be had and the trademark Sedaris take on people and awkward situations. But there were more than the usual number of characters in this selection that were acerbic and unlikable and some of the essays just fell flat for m</span>
  <span id="freeText4934933371849509458" style="display:none">In my binge listening to Sedaris lately, looking for laughs and something to lighten my day I didn't find this selection of essays as humorous as the 3 previous books. I even went through it a second time to be sure. There were definitely some funny moments and some chuckles to be had and the trademark Sedaris take on people and awkward situations. But there were more than the usual number of characters in this selection that were acerbic and unlikable and some of the essays just fell flat for me. I must blame myself entirely in terms of my high expectations and need for escapist fun during these trying times because Sedaris isn't only about escapist fun. So if you are a Sedaris fan you may want to ignore everything you just read and give this one a try.</span>
  <a data-text-id="4934933371849509458" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
